OL,3,CTribunal to probe claims of police
OL,4,Cspying on journalists
OL,6,FA judicial tribunal will later examine
OL,7,Fallegations of widespread police
OL,8,Fspying on journalists.
OL,10,FThe Investigatory Powers Tribunal
OL,11,F(IPT) in London is to probe claims
OL,12,Fthat investigative reporters in
OL,13,FNorthern Ireland were subject to
OL,14,Funlawful covert intelligence by the
OL,15,Fpolice.
OL,17,FThe actions of three police forces `
OL,18,Fthe Police Service of Northern
OL,19,FIreland, Durham Constabulary and the
OL,20,FMet Police ` are set to be scrutinised.
