OL,3,CTribunal to probe claims of police
OL,4,Cspying on journalists
OL,6,FA complaint was initially brought to
OL,7,Fthe IPT by documentary makers Barry
OL,8,FMcCaffrey and Trevor Birney, who were
OL,9,Fcontroversially arrested in 2018 as
OL,10,Fpart of a police investigation into
OL,11,Fthe alleged leaking of a confidential
OL,12,Fdocument that appeared in a film they
OL,13,Fmade on a Troubles massacre.
OL,15,FPreparatory hearings before the IPT
OL,16,Fsubsequently have heard further claims
OL,17,Fthat PSNI spying operations extended
OL,18,Fto several other reporters operating
OL,19,Fin the region.
