OL,3,CTribunal to probe claims of police
OL,4,Cspying on journalists
OL,6,FIn the case involving Mr Birney and Mr
OL,7,FMcCaffrey, the PSNI asked Durham
OL,8,FConstabulary to investigate the leak
OL,9,Fof a Police Ombudsman of Northern
OL,10,FIreland document that appeared in the
OL,11,Fdocumentary, No Stone Unturned, into
OL,12,Fthe 1994 loyalist paramilitary
OL,13,Fmassacre in the village of
OL,14,FLoughinisland in Co Down.
