OL,3,CTribunal to probe claims of police
OL,4,Cspying on journalists
OL,6,FGiven the ombudsman's role is to probe
OL,7,Fallegations of wrongdoing against
OL,8,Fpolice in Northern Ireland, the PSNI
OL,9,Fsaid it would have presented conflict
OL,10,Fof interest issues for it to have
OL,11,Ftaken on the leak probe, and therefore
OL,12,Fasked for Durham to lead on the case.
OL,14,FIn 2020, the High Court in Belfast
OL,15,Fruled that warrants secured by police
OL,16,Fto raid Mr McCaffrey and Mr Birney's
OL,17,Fhomes and business offices in Belfast
OL,18,Fwere wrongly obtained.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G4/10
