OL,4,Cspying on journalists
OL,6,FThe PSNI later unreservedly apologised
OL,7,Ffor how the men had been treated and
OL,8,Fagreed to pay #875,000 in damages to
OL,9,Fthe journalists and the film company
OL,10,Fbehind the documentary.
OL,12,FMr Birney and Mr McCaffrey lodged a
OL,13,Fcomplaint with the IPT asking it to
OL,14,Festablish whether there had been any
OL,15,Funlawful surveillance of them.
OL,17,FFormer Durham detective Darren Ellis,
OL,18,Fwho took a leading role in the
OL,19,Finvestigation, is set to be a key
OL,20,Fwitness before the tribunal.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G5/10
