OL,3,CTribunal to probe claims of police
OL,4,Cspying on journalists
OL,6,FAs well as the events around the
OL,7,Fdocumentary, the tribunal ` chaired by
OL,8,FLord Justice Singh ` has also been
OL,9,Fpresented with evidence related to two
OL,10,Fother instances of police surveillance
OL,11,Fagainst Mr McCaffrey in 2013 and 2011.
OL,13,FIn the 2011 incident, it is alleged
OL,14,Fthat the Met Police illegally obtained
OL,15,FMr McCaffrey's phone data ` material
OL,16,Fthe PSNI subsequently secured seven
OL,17,Fyears later as part of another probe
OL,18,Finto the reporter's work.
