OL,3,CTribunal to probe claims of police
OL,4,Cspying on journalists
OL,6,FEarlier this year, the BBC instructed
OL,7,Flawyers to contact the tribunal over
OL,8,Fclaims one of its ex-investigative
OL,9,Freporters was spied on by police.
OL,11,FThe allegations relate to former BBC
OL,12,Fjournalist Vincent Kearney and his
OL,13,Fwork on a 2011 Spotlight documentary
OL,14,Fthat probed the independence of the
OL,15,FPolice Ombudsman's office.
OL,17,FMr Kearney, who is the current
OL,18,Fnorthern editor at RTE, has said he is
OL,19,Fdetermined to find out what happened.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G7/10
