OL,3,CTribunal to probe claims of police
OL,4,Cspying on journalists
OL,6,FThe tribunal also heard claims that
OL,7,Fthe PSNI undertook six-monthly trawls
OL,8,Fof the phone data of "troublemaker"
OL,9,Fjournalists to see if they were in
OL,10,Fcontact with officer sources.
OL,12,FUnder pressure to address the claims
OL,13,Faired at the IPT, the PSNI published a
OL,14,Freport on its surveillance of
OL,15,Fjournalists in the summer.
OL,17,FThe report revealed that the PSNI had
OL,18,Fmade 323 applications for
OL,19,Fcommunications data relating to
OL,20,Fjournalists since 2011.
