OL,6,FHowever, it said the vast majority of
OL,7,Fapplications were related to
OL,8,Fjournalists who were victims, suspects
OL,9,For witnesses to crime.
OL,11,FThe report, which was compiled for the
OL,12,FNorthern Ireland Policing Board ` the
OL,13,FPSNI's oversight body ` said of the
OL,14,F323 applications, 10 sought to
OL,15,Fidentify a journalistic source using
OL,16,Fcovert powers.
