OL,3,CTribunal to probe claims of police
OL,4,Cspying on journalists
OL,6,FAs well as the report, PSNI Chief
OL,7,FConstable Jon Boutcher also announced
OL,8,Fan independent review, headed by Angus
OL,9,FMcCullough KC, of any use of
OL,10,Fsurveillance against journalists and
OL,11,Fother specific groups by police in
OL,12,FNorthern Ireland.
OL,14,FMr Boutcher has insisted much of the
OL,15,Fpublic concern over the spying claims
OL,16,Fhas arisen because of
OL,17,F"misinterpretation of documents" made
OL,18,Favailable in redacted form at the
OL,19,Ftribunal.
